WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.277 --> 00:00:02.860
(gentle music)

00:00:10.860 --> 00:00:14.483
- So we recommend taking
Fortagen 30 minutes before bed.

00:00:15.840 --> 00:00:19.640
Mostly because the majority
of protein synthesis

00:00:19.640 --> 00:00:21.860
that happens in the body happens at night.

00:00:21.860 --> 00:00:24.380
But that's just the
majority, not all of it.

00:00:24.380 --> 00:00:28.520
So, now, there's a lot
of different questions,

00:00:28.520 --> 00:00:32.510
I think based on people having habits.

00:00:32.510 --> 00:00:34.160
Like if you have a habit of having

00:00:34.160 --> 00:00:36.000
a protein shake after your workout,

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.190
I wanna be clear, there's no benefit

00:00:38.190 --> 00:00:41.520
to having protein after
a workout specifically,

00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:44.790
but if that's when you wanna
take your protein, okay,

00:00:44.790 --> 00:00:46.440
you can do that, that's fine.

00:00:46.440 --> 00:00:51.440
So, the two big rules
with timing Fortagen,

00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:56.470
is you wanna have it at least two hours

00:00:56.470 --> 00:00:59.130
after your last meal that included protein

00:00:59.130 --> 00:01:03.510
because sometimes, protein
takes a long time to digest

00:01:03.510 --> 00:01:05.930
and you don't want it
to conflict with some

00:01:05.930 --> 00:01:09.050
of the lower qualities of
protein in your nutrition.

00:01:09.050 --> 00:01:12.393
And by the way, everything is
lower quality than Fortagen.

00:01:13.230 --> 00:01:15.830
Two hours, remember that.

00:01:15.830 --> 00:01:18.990
And then if you wanna do more
than one dose of Fortagen,

00:01:18.990 --> 00:01:21.990
so let's say one dose of Fortagen makes up

00:01:21.990 --> 00:01:26.700
for the equivalent of 50
grams of other protein source.

00:01:26.700 --> 00:01:29.640
So like (mumbles) or something like that.

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:31.140
When you do that,

00:01:31.140 --> 00:01:35.090
you wanna wait 30 minutes
between the doses.

00:01:35.090 --> 00:01:37.400
At least 30 minutes.

00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:41.240
So, I take two doses a day,

00:01:41.240 --> 00:01:44.807
and then I still wanna get
like at least 200 grams,

00:01:47.120 --> 00:01:48.750
when on days that I eat

00:01:48.750 --> 00:01:50.200
'cause I don't eat every day.

00:01:51.720 --> 00:01:53.460
I wanna get at least 200 grams

00:01:53.460 --> 00:01:58.410
of natural source protein
meats, really is all I eat.

00:01:58.410 --> 00:02:02.920
So, when you do that,
you just wanna make sure

00:02:02.920 --> 00:02:06.990
that there's a 30 minute period
so that your body can absorb

00:02:06.990 --> 00:02:09.730
what had already, it
absorbes very quickly,

00:02:09.730 --> 00:02:11.870
30 minutes is a very short absorption time

00:02:11.870 --> 00:02:13.620
and then you can have another dose.

